recently_watched.Description: Love is a whimsical romantic comedy that delves into the intricacies and absurdities of modern relationships. Through the quirky and often tumultuous journey of its protagonists, the series explores the complexities of love, intimacy, and personal growth. With a blend of humor and heart, Love offers a refreshingly honest portrayal of the highs and lows of romance, reminding us that true love is often found in the most unexpected of places.
Follows the political rivalries and romance of Queen Elizabeth II's reign and the events that shaped the second half of the 20th century.
